{"tid":2246521,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Twitter認錯　重新容許用戶分享涉拜登政治報道","createTime":"2020-10-17T06:49:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T08:03:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"833203f560e1516b7452ae2ab49a8c824bac418c","tid":2246521,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:49:46.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n社交網站Twitter承認，之前限制用戶轉發《紐約郵報》一篇有關美國民主黨總統候選人拜登及他兒子的政治報道，是犯了錯誤，已重新容許分享文章。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter表示，報道中的個人資料，已被傳媒廣泛報道，並在各平台流傳，承認之前直接封鎖連結是錯誤做法，目前已經更新指引；除非被上傳的資料由黑客直接分享，否則不會刪除。<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555266-20201017.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555266-20201017.htm&d=6FpmejEDNbHOA1ae24haoxD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=27a51a50\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555266-20201017.htm&h=bba83e6d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555266-20201017.htm</a>"},{"pid":"42b2b0bfada9a8a619397ad977b9f15891bc6c55","tid":2246521,"uid":364850,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T06:50:58.000Z","msg":"明知侵侵係Twitter 超級Fans, <br />\n都要同侵侵過唔去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafb8f6d0932027da2e21b81e5456261a0067354","tid":2246521,"uid":285261,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"有無限制traffic 先"},{"pid":"9bee24e1bde5c7829321b690a928be29b4286c84","tid":2246521,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"Twitter又幫Trump助選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6a8a121d8a249336e1369455028cd6adcbe9b7","tid":2246521,"uid":296369,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-17T08:03:53.000Z","msg":"要check 下Twitter 有冇限t